query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from site AS s
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('superuser') AND t1.name IN ('command-line',
'hard-drive',
'linux',
'macos',
'microsoft-excel',
'networking',
'ubuntu',
'windows-7',
'wireless-networking')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name IN ('Analytical',
'Announcer',
'Benefactor',
'Enlightened',
'Guru',
'Investor',
'Quorum',
'Taxonomist')
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 10
inner join question AS q1
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND q1.id = a1.question_id AND q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 0 AND q1.favorite_count <= 1
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id;
